      {
        "element": "p",
        "class": "",
        "text": "wherefore I have brought him before you; the whole company then present: ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "p",
        "class": "",
        "text": "and especially before thee, O King Agrippa; as being not only a man of eminence, dignity, and authority, but of knowledge in such matters, which the Jews accused Paul of; see Acts 26:2. ",
        "children": [
          {
            "element": "span",
            "class": "",
            "text": "and especially before thee, O King Agrippa; as being not only a man of eminence, dignity, and authority, but of knowledge in such matters, which the Jews accused Paul of; see ",
